commentPostTextItems.html: TV umpire is called for and the red light flashes, 2 runs victory for Aussies
Aussies win by 2 runs and with that they bag the Chappell-Hadlee Trophy, 2005-06
Please join us for the last match of this series on 10th to be played at Christchurch

milestones.description: Symonds and Clarke's 220-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 172 between Michael Bevan and Lehmann
Symonds has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (96) in an innings in ODIs for AUS, going past Hayden's 84
